highlights.text: “מה עשית לי” by Eden Hason is the highest new entry on Top Songs Israel at #85.
Omer Adam has the most spots on Top Songs Israel. “ראיתי עולם” is the highest at #3.
“רק אל תלכי” by Zikney Tzfat is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Israel, up 52 spots at #145.
“לשוב הביתה” by Ishay Ribo has been on Top Songs Israel the longest, at 329 weeks straight.
